{
  "EvelynRepeteable": "Zdravstvuy, dorogoy!^Segodnya ya podumala o tebe i zahotela otpravit nebolshoy podarok.^^Nadeyus, chto on podarit tebe nemnogo radosti.^Spasibo, chto ty takoy prekrasnyy drug.^^S lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.1": "Zdravstvuy, dorogoy.^Ya zametila, kak mnogo ty trudishsya na ferme v poslednee vremya.^Kogda ya navodila poryadok v shkafu, to nashla eti ostavshiesya semena.^^Uverena, chto na tvoey ferme im budet gorazdo luchshe.^Tolko ne zabyvay nemnogo otdykhat tozhe.^^S lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.2": "Zdravstvuy snova!^Mne vsegda stanovitsya radostno, kogda ya vizhu, kak ty prokhodish mimo nashego malenkogo doma.^Dzhordzh govorit, chto emu vse ravno, no ya znayu, chto on rad tvoim vizitam.^^Ya vybrala dlya tebya eti lukovitsy tsvetov, chtoby tvoya ferma stala eshche krasivee.^Nadeyus, oni rastsvetut tak zhe prekrasno, kak nasha druzhba.^^S lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.3": "Dorogoy,^Tsvety u moego okna rastsveli i napomnili mne o tebe.^Tak priyatno videt, kak krepnet nasha druzhba.^^Ya posylayu tebe neskolko moikh lyubimykh semyan.^Beregi ikh, i oni obyazatelno prinesut mnogo radosti tvoey ferme.^^S lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.4": "Zdravstvuy!^Pogoda menyaetsya, i sad trebuet mnogo zaboty, no dlya khoroshikh druzey vsegda naydetsya vremya.^^Nadeyus, eti semena napolnyat tvoyu fermu prekrasnymi tsvetami i priyatnym aromatom.^Kogda oni rastsvetut, nadeyus, ty vspomnish obo mne.^^Krepko obnimayu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.5": "Nadeyus, u tebya vse khorosho.^Ya beregla eto redkoe semya dlya osobogo sluchaya, no ponyala, chto net luchshego momenta, chtoby poblagodarit tebya za tvoyu druzhbu.^^Ya takzhe prigotovila dlya tebya ukrashenie iz sushenykh podsolnukhov.^Uverena, ono sdelaet tvoy dom eshche uyutnee.^^S lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.6": "Zdravstvuy, dorogoy.^Na ferme vsegda stolko raboty, chto inogda ty, navernoe, zabyvayesh otdykhat i khorosho est.^^Poetomu ya prigotovila dlya tebya sytnyy obed, chtoby ty mog vzyat ego s soboy segodnya.^Obeshchay mne, chto budesh zabotitsya i o sebe, khorosho?^^Krepko obnimayu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.7": "Dorogoy,^Segodnya utrom ya byla na kukhne, i zapakh risovogo pudinga napomnil mne o tebe.^^Ya otlozhila dlya tebya odnu portsiyu,^a vmeste s ney i malenkoe rastenie, kotoroe nedavno peresadila.^Uverena, ono prekrasno budet smotretsya na tvoey verande.^^S lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.8": "Zdravstvuy!^Segodnya ya prigotovila nachinku, kotoruyu Dzhordzh tak lyubit, i, kak obychno, prigotovila slishkom mnogo.^Poetomu ya otlozhila dlya tebya khoroshuyu portsiyu.^^Ya takzhe posylayu tebe rastenie iz moego sada.^Ono menyaetsya vmeste so vremenami goda i vsegda vyzyvaet u menya ulybku. Nadeyus, ono poraduet i tebya.^^Krepko obnimayu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.9": "Dorogoy,^Ya prigotovila partiyu klyukvennykh sladostey i otlozhila samye vkusnye dlya tebya.^^Ya nashla eto ukrashenie v starom sunduke i podumala, chto ono idealno podoydet dlya tvoego uyutnogo doma.^Spasibo, chto prinosish stolko radosti nashey malenkoi derevne.^^S lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin",
  "evelyn.10": "Ya ne mogu peredat slovami, kak silno ty izmenil nashi zhizni k luchshemu.^My s Dzhordzhem iskrenne schitaem tebya chlenom nashey semyi.^^Ya ispekla svoy luchshiy tort dlya prazdnika i prigotovila dlya tebya etot prekrasnyy tsvetochnyy gorshok.^V nashem dome tebya vsegda budet zhdat teploe i uyutnoe mesto.^^So vsey moey lyubovyu,^- Babushka Evelin"
}